{"tid":749601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【企債出事】罕見一周連環債券違約！人民幣票據爆煲","createTime":"2018-07-20T07:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T09:13:44.000Z","uid":54373,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"26b827f913186973960741c823f65f48d267f384","tid":749601,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T07:22:02.000Z","msg":"《証券日報》報道，繼7月16日「15中城建MTN001」發生違約之後，上海清算所日前發佈的公告顯示，博源控股2013年度第一期中期票據（「13博源MTN001」）未按期足額償付本息，發生8億元人民幣的中期票據違約。至此，今年以來債券市場已發生28宗違約事件，違約債券餘額已達291.87億元人民幣，涉及發行人共16家。對於債券市場而言，一周內傳出兩宗債券違約的消息並非常見。<br />\n<br />\n對於此次「13博源MTN001」如預期般「爆雷」，業內人士反應較為平淡。某券商固收分析人士指出，該債券的發行人已是既有違約主體，之前違約的債券仍未解決完畢，更難以籌措此次債券的兌付資金，違約也是意料之中的事。"},{"pid":"d6887a5d735fbece110240ddf6c11a9d168c36df","tid":749601,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T07:25:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09645e864393bb7accd7168a6ed5bf0fb5de56cc","tid":749601,"uid":22422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T07:26:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>債轉股<br />\n鎂轉冥</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1fe991a1df701244d8a94b84f71796a587667d4","tid":749601,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T07:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ccbf532f1674855432fe0bba45e11814cb0aa8","tid":749601,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T07:28:12.000Z","msg":"5毛：又話支爆 爆未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年以來債券市場已發生28宗違約事件"},{"pid":"ddf542927